quran[70]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,“Chakudza cha choonadi (chomwe ndi Qiyâma)
  69,2,“Kodi chakudza cha choonadi nchiyani
  69,3,“Nanga nchiyani chikudziwitse za chakudza cha choonadicho
  69,4,“Asamudu ndi Âdi adatsutsa zakudza kwa Qiyâma (yomwe idzadzidzimutsa zolengedwa mwamphamvu ndi zoopsa zake)
  69,5,"“Tsono Asamudu adaonongedwa ndi phokoso lopyola muyeso, (lamphamvu kwambiri)"
  69,6,"“Ndipo Âdi adaonongedwa ndi chimphepo cha mkuntho, chozizira, champhamvu kwambiri"
  69,7,“Allah adachitumiza kwa iwo pa usiku usanu ndi uwiri ndi masana asanu ndi atatu mosadukiza; kotero ukadawaona ali lambalamba mmenemo ngati mathunthu a mitengo ya kanjedza yopanda kanthu m’kati mwake
  69,8,“Kodi nanga ukumuona wotsala mwa iwo
  69,9,"“Ndipo Firiaun ndi amene adalipo iye asadabadwe, ndi khamu la anthu amidzi yotembenuzidwa (anthu a Luti) adadza ndi machimo (akulu)"
  69,10,“Ndipo (yense wa iwowa) adanyoza Mtumiki wa Mbuye wawo; choncho adawalanga chilango chopitilira muyeso
  69,11,“Ndithu pamene madzi adasefukira mopyola muyeso (mpaka kumeza mapiri nthawi ya chigumula cha Nowa) Ife tidakukwezani mchombo choyandama ndi kuyenda
  69,12,"“Kuti tichichite (chochitikacho chomwe okhulupirira adapulumuka nacho; osakhulupirira adaonongeka nacho) kukhala lingaliro ndi phunziro kwa inu, ndikuti lisunge (nkhaniyi) khutu losunga"
  69,13,"“Choncho likadzaimbidwa lipenga, kuimba kumodzi kokha (zamoyo zonse zidzafa)"
  69,14,“Ndipo nthaka ndi mapiri nkuchotsedwa m’malo mwake ndi kuphwanyidwa kamodzi nkamodzi
  69,15,"“Chomwecho tsiku limenelo, chochitika chidzachitika (imene ili Qiyâma)"
  69,16,“Ndipo thambo lidzasweka choncho ilo tsiku limenelo lidzakhala lofooka (pamene lidali lolimba)
  69,17,"“Ndipo angelo adzakhala m’mphepete mwake, ndipo pamwamba pawo tsiku limenero (angelo) asanu ndi atatu adzasenza Arsh (Mpando wachifumu) ya Mbuye wako"
  69,18,“Tsiku limenelo mudzabweretsedwa ku chiweruzo; sichidzabisika chilichonse chobisika mwa inu
  69,19,"“Tsono amene adzapatsidwa kaundula wake chakudzanja lakumanja kwake adzanena (mokondwa kwa amene ali m’phepete mwake): “Tengani! Werengani kaundula wanga!”"
  69,20,““Ndithudi ine ndidatsimikiza (pa dziko lapansi) kuti ndidzakumana ndi chiwerengero changa.”
  69,21,"“Choncho, iye adzakhala m’moyo wosangalatsa"
  69,22,“M’munda wapamwamba
  69,23,“Zipatso zake zoyandikira pansi (zosavuta kuzithyola)
  69,24,"“(Adzawauza kuti:) “Idyani, ndipo imwani mosangalala pa zimene mudatsogoza mmasiku aja adapita (a pa dziko lapansi).”"
  69,25,"“Ndipo amene adzapatsidwe kaundula wake kudzanja lake lamanzere, adzanena (modandaula): “Kalanga ine! Ndiponi ndikadapanda kupatsidwa kaundula wangayu!”"
  69,26,““Nkusadziwa chiwerengero changa!”
  69,27,““Ha! imfa ija ikadandimaliziratu (ndi kundilekanitsa ine ndi zimenezi).”
  69,28,““Chuma changa sichidandithandize!”
  69,29,““Mphamvu zanga (ndi moyo wanga wathanzi) zandichokera!”
  69,30,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa angelo oyang’anira Jahena): Mgwireni ndipo mnjateni (pomphatikiza manja ndi khosi)"
  69,31,“Kenako mponyeni ku Moto
  69,32,“Kenakonso mulowetseni mtcheni lotalika mikwamba makumi asanu ndi awiri
  69,33,"“Ndithudi, iye sadali kukhulupirira mwa Allah wamkulu"
  69,34,“Sadalinso kulimbikitsa zodyetsa osauka
  69,35,"“Basi, lero kuno alibe bwenzi (lomthandiza)"
  69,36,“Ngakhale chakudya kupatula mafinya (a anthu a ku Moto)
  69,37,“Zomwe palibe angazidye kupatula ochimwa (mwadala)
  69,38,“Choncho ndikulumbilira zimene mukuziona
  69,39,“Ndi zimene simukuziona
  69,40,“Ndithudi iyi (Qur’an) ndiliwu la mthenga wolemekezeka (Jibril)
  69,41,"“Ndipo simawu a mlakatuli, ndi zochepa zimene mukuzikhulupirira"
  69,42,"“Ndiponso simawu a mlosi, ndizochepa zimene mmakumbukira"
  69,43,“(Ichi ndi) chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Mbuye wa zolengedwa
  69,44,“Ndipo (Mneneri) akadatipekera bodza linalake
  69,45,“Tikadamgwira (mwamphamvu) ndimkono wamanja
  69,46,“Ndipo tikadadula mwa iye mtsempha wa moyo (kotero kuti ndikuferatu nthawi yomweyo)
  69,47,“Sipakadapezeka aliyense mwa inu womteteza (kuchilango Chathu)
  69,48,“Ndithu iyi (Qur’an) ndi phunziro labwino kwa owopa (Allah)
  69,49,"“Ndithu Ife, tikudziwa kuti ena mwa inu ndiotsutsa (Qur’an)"
  69,50,“Ndipo ndithu iyi (Qur’an) idzakhala chowadandaulitsa (chachikulu) osakhulupirira (pamene adzaona chilango chawo ndi mtendere wa okhulupirira)
  69,51,“Ndithu iyoyi ndichoonadi Chotsimikizika; (mulibe chikaiko)
  69,52,"“Basi, lemekeza dzina la Mbuye wako Wamkulu (pitiriza kutamanda dzina Lake)"
  70,1,"“Wopempha adapempha kuti chiwadzere msanga chilango chopezekacho, (m’kupempha kwa chipongwe ndi kotsutsa)"
  70,2,“Kwa okanira palibe angachitsekereze
  70,3,“Chochokera kwa Allah Mwini makwelero
  70,4,“Angelo ndi Jiburil amakwera kwa Iye (Allah) m’tsiku lomwe kutalika kwake kuli ngati zaka zikwi makumi asanu
  70,5,"“Choncho, pirira (iwe Mtumiki (s.a.w) kupirira kwabwino"
  70,6,“Ndithu iwo akuliona (tsiku la Qiyâma) kuti lili kutali (silingachitike)
  70,7,“Koma Ife tikuliona kuti lilipafupi (ndilochitika)
  70,8,“Tsiku limene thambo lidzakhala ngati mtovu wosungunuka
  70,9,“Ndipo mapiri adzakhala ngati ubweya (wongouluka wokha)
  70,10,“Ndipo m’bale sadzafunsa za m’bale wake
  70,11,“Ngakhale adzawalole kuti aonane ndi kudziwana pakati pawo (sadzafunsana). Wochimwa adzalakalaka kuti akadaziwombola ku chilango cha tsiku limenelo ndi ana ake
  70,12,"“Ndi mkazi wake, ndi m’bale wake"
  70,13,“Ndi akumtundu wake amene amamsunga
  70,14,"“Ndi (kulipira) zonse za m’dziko, kuti zimpulumutse"
  70,15,"“Iyayi, (siya iwe wamachimo zimene ukulakalakazo)! Ndithu umenewu ndi Moto wa malawi"
  70,16,“Wosupula mwamphamvu khungu
  70,17,“Udzaitana (potchula dzina la aliyense) amene adachitembenuzira msana choona ndi kunyoza
  70,18,“Adasonkhanitsa (chuma) ndi kusunga (m’nkhokwe zake popanda kuperekera chopereka cha Allah)